data.description: Step through the doors of this modern manufactured masterpiece and be greeted by a seamless open-concept layout, illuminated by ample recessed lighting and complemented by soaring vaulted ceilings. The kitchen, adorned with hardwood cabinetry and a high-end backsplash sets a perfect stage for memorable meals. Retreat to the main suite, where a full bathroom awaits, featuring an exquisite stone shower that offers both luxury and comfort. Rest assured in the warmth and comfort of a newly installed HVAC system, ensuring year-round comfort.Beyond its stylish interiors, this home sits on an expansive lot of nearly half an acre. Whether you dream of creating a vibrant garden, having ample space for your vehicles, or cultivating your favorite plants, the possibilities here are endless.Experience the tranquility of Tieton living, all while enjoying the convenience of nearby amenities. Don't miss this opportunity to own a slice of Tieton serenity! Contact us or your preferred real estate agent today to book a viewing. Your dream home awaits!
